<span id="freeTextContainer5999467742914274871">Three stories presented as gently as a whisper, slipping away just as softly. Omens of sleep and the sweet voice of final rest, the warmth of dreamless voyages in the night. Images of the lonely and disfigured spirits, walking pale in haunted visages, grasping at blooming flesh. We end void of answers or solace, mourning the consequences of the space of our unconscious, the hidden valleys of pain beneath the folds of clothing and skin, our immutable desires, and our eternal woe at their irresolu</span>
  <span id="freeText5999467742914274871" style="display:none">Three stories presented as gently as a whisper, slipping away just as softly. Omens of sleep and the sweet voice of final rest, the warmth of dreamless voyages in the night. Images of the lonely and disfigured spirits, walking pale in haunted visages, grasping at blooming flesh. We end void of answers or solace, mourning the consequences of the space of our unconscious, the hidden valleys of pain beneath the folds of clothing and skin, our immutable desires, and our eternal woe at their irresolution.</span>
