<span id="freeTextContainer3685848909861788651">House of the Sleeping beauties is a novella of astonishing beauty and delicacy. This volume contains two other very short stories which I did not read. But &apos;House&apos; is as fine and perfect a work as is Snow Country.</span>
  <span id="freeText3685848909861788651" style="display:none">House of the Sleeping beauties is a novella of astonishing beauty and delicacy. This volume contains two other very short stories which I did not read. But 'House' is as fine and perfect a work as is Snow Country.</span>
